Introduction

Choi Soobin is a South Korean singer-songwriter, and composer under BIGHIT MUSIC and HYBE Labels. He is best known as the leader of the boy group TXT.

On January 13, 2019, Soobin was revealed as the second member of TXT (Tomorrow X Together). He made his official debut with the group on March 4, 2019, through their mini-album "The Dream Chapter: STAR".
